287
00:19:13,920 --> 00:19:17,400
Leaning on the window, how can I pass the time till night alone?

288
00:19:17,880 --> 00:19:19,760
The drizzle falls on the buttonwood trees.

289
00:19:20,040 --> 00:19:22,560
Rain-drops drip down at dusk.

290
00:19:23,070 --> 00:19:26,680
As a time like this, what immense sorrow I must bear!

291
00:19:29,190 --> 00:19:32,160
I always feel that he will go to a bigger

292
00:19:32,350 --> 00:19:33,830
and broader world.

293
00:19:35,310 --> 00:19:36,710
By his light,

294
00:19:37,520 --> 00:19:39,830
I've also glimpsed what the broad world looks like.

295
00:19:41,520 --> 00:19:42,800
I come to realize

296
00:19:43,710 --> 00:19:45,520
that I also want to go there.

297
00:19:46,710 --> 00:19:48,190
