323
00:21:34,560 --> 00:21:35,760
Monthly test is coming.

324
00:21:35,920 --> 00:21:37,400
I should be fully prepared.

325
00:21:42,520 --> 00:21:44,560
When did you two hang out together?

326
00:21:47,400 --> 00:21:48,430
Hello. May I help you?

327
00:21:48,430 --> 00:21:49,400
Two lemonades.

328
00:21:49,830 --> 00:21:50,350
Okay.

329
00:21:57,070 --> 00:21:59,710
