352
00:22:47,800 --> 00:22:48,520
You're welcome.

353
00:22:52,350 --> 00:22:53,310
Why are you here?

354
00:22:53,310 --> 00:22:54,350
Why didn't you say hello to me?

355
00:22:58,310 --> 00:22:59,430
Let me sip yours. I'm dying of thirst!

356
00:22:59,590 --> 00:23:00,470
Buy it by yourself!

357
00:23:01,230 --> 00:23:02,040
I'll drink…

358
00:23:03,950 --> 00:23:05,000
Song Ziqi

359
00:23:07,160 --> 00:23:08,280
What's wrong by drinking yours?

360
00:23:08,280 --> 00:23:09,190
How stingy you are!

361
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:14,830
Thank you.

362
00:23:16,560 --> 00:23:17,710
