363
00:23:17,880 --> 00:23:18,710
Go back yourself.

364
00:23:18,950 --> 00:23:20,230
I'll go with Keke today.

365
00:23:23,280 --> 00:23:24,000
Alright.

366
00:23:24,160 --> 00:23:25,800
I'll go alone. Bye-bye.

367
00:23:41,590 --> 00:23:42,520
Do you think

368
00:23:43,400 --> 00:23:45,470
