418
00:26:10,000 --> 00:26:10,880
Xianxian

419
00:26:11,070 --> 00:26:12,280
Shadi, Keke.

420
00:26:12,470 --> 00:26:13,280
Come in.

421
00:26:16,680 --> 00:26:17,760
