455
00:27:36,310 --> 00:27:37,350
Try it on.

456
00:27:40,350 --> 00:27:41,230
Hang on.

457
00:27:43,280 --> 00:27:44,350
What's the matter again?

458
00:27:44,880 --> 00:27:46,760
What's wrong with your jarhead?

459
00:27:47,800 --> 00:27:48,880
