460
00:27:49,710 --> 00:27:51,230
Of course it's her who is to blame!

461
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:56,160
Alright. Let me handle it for you.

462
00:27:56,190 --> 00:27:57,040
Let's go!

463
00:27:57,590 --> 00:27:58,280
How will you fix it?

464
00:27:58,640 --> 00:28:00,470
I'll help you to trim your jarhead.

465
00:28:01,310 --> 00:28:02,760
Will it become…

466
00:28:16,950 --> 00:28:18,760
If you keep doing it, I'll go back!

467
00:28:21,000 --> 00:28:21,800
It's the most boring birthday

468
00:28:21,830 --> 00:28:24,110
I've ever celebrated!

469
00:28:24,800 --> 00:28:27,280
How miserable I am!

470
00:28:29,470 --> 00:28:31,520
Well… How about shopping?

471
00:28:32,350 --> 00:28:33,280
Boring.

472
00:28:33,430 --> 00:28:34,400
How about the amusement park?

473
00:28:35,230 --> 00:28:36,590
Boring.

474
00:28:38,640 --> 00:28:39,640
