475
00:28:39,640 --> 00:28:40,760
I want a buzz.

476
00:28:41,000 --> 00:28:42,230
I want a party.

477
00:28:42,590 --> 00:28:45,800
I want him to hang out with me!

478
00:28:52,760 --> 00:28:54,190
I know you are all here.

479
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:58,230
Aren't you celebrating your birthday?

480
00:28:58,590 --> 00:28:59,190
