503
00:29:52,680 --> 00:29:54,350
I'm afraid I'll spoil your spirits.

504
00:29:54,800 --> 00:29:56,110
After the monthly test,

505
00:29:56,110 --> 00:29:57,160
I guarantee that I'll make it up to you.

506
00:29:57,520 --> 00:29:58,280
I swear.

507
00:29:59,680 --> 00:30:00,880
Just let her go home.

508
00:30:01,040 --> 00:30:02,110
