509
00:30:03,760 --> 00:30:04,640
Alright.

510
00:30:05,230 --> 00:30:07,040
Be careful when you go back home.

511
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:08,190
We'll go now.

512
00:30:08,190 --> 00:30:08,710
Okay.

513
00:30:08,950 --> 00:30:09,560
Bye-bye.

514
00:30:10,230 --> 00:30:10,880
Bye-bye.

515
00:30:18,680 --> 00:30:19,880
Zhou Siyue

