526
00:30:58,430 --> 00:30:59,000
Okay.

527
00:31:01,110 --> 00:31:01,520
Here's your change.

528
00:31:01,560 --> 00:31:02,040
Hold it.

529
00:31:02,230 --> 00:31:02,920
Okay. Thank you.

530
00:31:04,310 --> 00:31:05,520
